All the creations in my shop are handmade with conventional home use sewing machines and sergers and as such it is recommended that all items are handwashed with a mild detergent in cool water and line dried. It is not recommended to wash your items in a washing machine or dryer; however, if you choose to do so, please keep a few things in mind. Always wash in cold water and air dry with no heat to avoid shrinkage and increase the life of your items. Items made with lace should always be handwashed and hung to dry, as lace is extremely delicate. Description:
Custom made personalized soap stamp or soap embossing die, engraved hard PVC mounted with a wood handle under 3"

Please contact me, before place order.

Good to know your location if a postage price is required.
*********************************************************
Note about Artwork: Generally, a vector format image (.eps .ai .cdr .svg) is required to make the stamp. If you only have your graphic in a bitmap format (.jpg .bmp .png .tif) I MIGHT be able to use it, but if I can't, it will need to be re-drawn. When ordering a stamp, please e-mail your graphic or logo in a vector format to me at: halasz66 [!at] gmail.com and if you do not have it in a vector format, send whatever you have and I will take a look at it. If you don't have ANY artwork, but have an idea of what you want, please send me a message.
We don't change the aspect ratio of your image. Nonetheless if you want to change the original look of design please let me know.
We make the stamp within 72 hours FROM DATE OF address confirmation AND approval of digital proof (not from order date).

Benefits of Japanese invisible resin clip-on earrings/ Ω Omega clip earrings:
1/  They are comfy & secured to wear hours long: Unlike the traditional bulky/heavy metal clip-ons that may pinch too hard/add weight to the whole earrings and hurt your earlobes, these clips are comfortably soft. Hence, they securely hug your earlobes without hurting them. You may not feel that you’re wearing clip-ons at all ! (however, you can still feel the weight of the actual earrings themselves). These resin invisible clip earrings will stay on & are comfy at the same time.
2/   The resin clips are “stealth”: The body of the clips are designed to be so minimal, so sophisticate & translucent ==  they blend with most skin tones. As the results, they “disappear” and it looks like you are wearing pierced earrings. ***Word of caution: these resin clip-on parts could be fragile. So please handle them with care. Try not to open them too wide & do not twist them***.
3/    They are safer for metal allergy people because the frame of the clips are resin. 
They are also safer for other people because long/dangle pierced earrings may get caught on something and rip your ears ( This actually happened to one of my older aunts when she was young and loved to wear dangle pierced earrings. All the women in my family stop wearing drop/dangle pierced earrings because of that incident. And the story is still being told for preventing purpose in our family/extended family ). In the same situation, a bad thing ( hopefully the only thing) that could happen to you when wearing clip-on earrings is losing your….. earrings. And losing a couple pairs of earrings is so much cheaper & certainly less painful than having your earlobes ripped. My apologies for the graphic details!!! 
These clip-on earrings are also called:
1/ Resin clip earrings ( the frame of the clips are made of resin).
2/ Invisible clip on earrings ( The frame of the clips are so minimal, so sophisticated & translucent so they will blend with most skin colors. Hence, it looks like you are wearing pierced earrings).
3/ Omega clip earrings  (they look like the Ω sign).
